category: Devel
requires: bash perl autoconf autoconf2.5 coreutils xz m4 texinfo alternatives
sdesc: "(1.12) a tool for generating GNU-compliant Makefiles"
ldesc: "This is Automake, a Makefile generator.  It was inspired
by the 4.4BSD make and include files, but aims to be portable and
to conform to the GNU standards for Makefile variables and targets.

Automake1.12 contains automake-1.12.x, and may be installed alongside
other versions such as automake1.6, automake1.8, etc."

